judges: Before Maxey, C. J., Drew, Linn, Stern, Patterson, Stearne and Jones, JJ.

opinions.text:
Per Curiam,
There is no merit in this appeal. The few questions raised are fully and correctly answered in the opinion of President Judge Bok of the learned court below. On that opinion the judgment appealed from is affirmed.
Judgment affirmed.
